{"tid":2162392,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"f(x)恐全走光！Krystal爆離開11年SM娛樂　「演員經紀公司瘋狂邀約」將有新出發","createTime":"2020-08-18T06:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T10:46:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d93f80f3ed55afe81153ebcbb9db8b85ed08f8","tid":2162392,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:06:03.000Z","msg":"韓團f(x)繼Victoria（宋茜）、Amber和Luna不續約後，小小年紀就進入SM娛樂當練習生的Krystal（鄭秀晶）18日也爆出將離開這個待了至少11年的公司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5078/5078951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5078%2F5078951.jpg&h=33f0de86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Krystal外型相當亮眼。（圖／翻攝自Krystal IG）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《日間體育》報導，相關人士透露：「Krystal將離開已經待了10幾年的SM娛樂，準備全新出發。」而且她已經和南韓國內許多有名的演員公司接洽討論，離開SM娛樂消息傳開後也有許多經紀公司主動提出簽約，到目前還沒有確定她的未來動向。對此，SM娛樂表示：「和Krystal的合約在8月到期，關於續約與否將會繼續和Krystal討論。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Krystal於2009年以5人組的偶像團體f(x)出道，擁有《LA chA TA》、《Danger》、《Hot Summer》和《Electric Shock》等熱門歌曲，2011年參演喜劇《Highkick3短腿的反擊》，後續在《繼承者們》、《機智牢房生活》和《對我而言可愛的她》等戲劇中的自然演技叫人印象深刻。"},{"pid":"9001441a749af14eb4c0de8458029f42f494981c","tid":2162392,"uid":152432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"全走光<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05bf1bd1b0d970b787beab2695c37f2d4a58c0b","tid":2162392,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"韓國女團F(x)走光圖"},{"pid":"e4469ff2c398550e062ee0182c19712234357d38","tid":2162392,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"想佢同姐姐一齊唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d9e722d21b39f9258c9a2f73cc42c4bdc70257","tid":2162392,"uid":68661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"f(x)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}